00:01:19.201 --> 00:01:26.544
until you get to a
quantity where there's no

00:01:26.544 --> 00:01:30.143
economic profit left.
Right over here, the way

00:01:30.143 --> 00:01:32.653
I've drawn it, the demand curve intersects

00:01:32.653 --> 00:01:35.745
the average total cost
curve right over here,

00:01:35.745 --> 00:01:38.211
