00:01:38.211 --> 00:01:39.792
We're producing a good quantity.

00:01:39.792 --> 00:01:42.205
It looks like it's
about 75 units combined;

00:01:42.205 --> 00:01:44.807
75 units for the whole market.

00:01:44.807 --> 00:01:48.171
But at this point, the market price

00:01:48.171 --> 00:01:51.013
is equal to the average total cost,

00:01:51.013 --> 00:01:53.458
